### Upload HTML → PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/html-to-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.html"
Content-Type: text/html

< ../fixtures/sample.html
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/5942609e0dc5407386775db4a330d9dc

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/5942609e0dc5407386775db4a330d9dc/download
